## Secure SSH Access

Port 22 is always closed. It only opens temporarily during GitHub Actions deployment.

How it works:

1. Workflow starts and gets GitHub Actions current public IP
2. Adds that IP to EC2 Security Group port 22
3. SSHs into EC2 and deploys the code
4. Removes that IP from Security Group immediately after
5. Port 22 is closed again

This means no one can SSH into your EC2 except during an active deployment. ✅

